Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:05.40,Default_Top - Copy,F,0,0,0,,{The girl who wished to read \Nlots of books, even after death,}Cô gái ước rằng mình được đọc thật nhiều sách ngay cả khi chết,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:10.00,Default_Top - Copy,F,0,0,0,,{began a new life in this world as Main, \Nthe daughter of a struggling family.}đã được chuyển sinh sang một thế giới khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If only I had a book to read...}Nếu có sách để đọc thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:16.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, as long as I have books,}Phải rồi, miễn là có sách,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.25,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can deal with things no matter where I am.}dù có khó khăn cỡ nào mình cũng chịu được.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.25,Default_Top - Copy,F,0,0,0,,{However, books are extremely \Nexpensive in this world.}Nhưng sách ở thế giới này vô cùng đắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.88,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Hey, do you know a shop that \Nsells books? Where is it?}Chú ơi, chú có biết nhà sách ở đâu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:30.13,Default,G,0,0,0,,{A shop? There isn't one.}Nhà sách? Làm gì có?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:34.24,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Books have to be copied by hand, you see.}Vì sách được sao chép bằng tay mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.15,Default,G,0,0,0,,{They cost so much money that \Nvery few people can buy any.}Nó tốn rất nhiều tiền bạc nên hiếm có người mua lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.59,Default_Top - Copy,F,0,0,0,,{And so, she came to a resolution...}Và cô gái đã nghĩ ra một giải pháp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.98,Default_Top - Copy,F,0,0,0,,{If she couldn't get any books to read, \Nshe'd just have to make them herself.}Nếu không có sách để đọc thì tự viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.78,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna make a book.}Mình sẽ viết sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.43,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{My very own book.}Một cuốn sách của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.84,Title,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:22.10,Title2,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:33.00,Ep Title,Ep Title,0,0,0,,{Chapter Two\NLife Improvements and Slates}Chương 2: Cải thiện cuộc sống và bảng viết
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Forget it. I don't care what it takes.}Mình không thể kén chọn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna get my books,\Nif it's the last thing I do!}Phải làm mọi cách để có sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I won't let this world beat me!}Mình sẽ không chịu thua!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.61,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But where do I buy paper?}Nhưng mua giấy ở đây bây giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:50.54,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, maybe I can find out by \Nsearching Main's memories.}A, thử xem lại kí ức của nhỏ này xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:56.60,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Paper, paper, paper...}Giấy, giấy, giấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Nope! I don't have any memories \Npertaining to paper!}Không được! Chẳng có kí ức nào cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:08.20,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And my hair feels like\Nsandpaper! It's so itchy!}Và tóc mình ngày càng ngứa nữa chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.20,Default_Top,T,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Con về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.69,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Welcome back, Turi. Thank you.}Con vất vả rồi, Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.82,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{This world doesn't have \Nany books or schools.}Thế giới này không có sách và cả trường học.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.90,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Kids here either help out with \Nhousework or go to work.}Trẻ con giúp việc nhà hoặc đi làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Mom.}Mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I got to pick a bunch of meryl fruit today.}Con lấy được nhiều trái Meryl lắm nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Looks like an avocado.}Giống trái bơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.71,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Let's extract the oil from \Nthem while they're fresh.}Hãy ép dầu khi chúng còn tươi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Get things ready, Turi.}Chuẩn bị đi con.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oil? You can extract oil from meryl fruit?}Dầu? Có thể ép dầu từ trái Meryl à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah, why?}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can make shampoo!}Mình có thể làm dầu gội!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.01,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Life improvement.}Cải thiện cuộc sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yahoo!}Ya hú!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I can wash my hair for the \Nfirst time in a week!}Mình có thể gội đầu sau 1 tuần rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:53.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{When I was Urano, I made lots of homemade \Nsoaps and shampoos with my mother,}Khi còn là Urano, mình đã làm rất nhiều dầu gội và xà bông với mẹ,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.04,Default,M,0,0,0,,{so I know how to do it.}nên biết cách làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If I extract the oil from a fruit,}Chiết xuất dầu từ trái cây,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{use some herbs for fragrance, \Nand add a pinch of salt...}bỏ thêm thảo mộc tạo mùi thơm và cho ít muối...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.75,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I should have my very own shampoo!}Mình có thể tạo ra dầu gội!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,{May I have some meryl fruit?}Cho em ít trái Meryl nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.81,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'd like to extract oil for myself.}Em cũng muốn ép dầu thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:14.32,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You want to try it, too?}Em muốn làm hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:14.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.26,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Listen up.}Nghe nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:20.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You have to wrap it in cloth \Nso it doesn't splatter...}Em phải bỏ nó vào vải trước, không là văng tứ tung...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.66,Default,T,0,0,0,,{M-Main? What do you think you're doing?}M-Myne? Em đang làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:33.76,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I see. I should've wrapped it \Nin cloth so it didn't splatter.}Hiểu rồi, phải bỏ nó vào vải để không văng à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.14,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Main?}Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.34,Default,E,0,0,0,,{No playing with food!}Không phá đồ ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{All done!}Xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main, the water's all boiled now.}Myne, nước xong rồi né.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,{That smells amazing.}Thơm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.26,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?!}Em làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,Rửa tóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.75,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:11.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Why does your hair look \Nlike the night sky now?}Sao tóc em trông như bầu trời đêm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What did you just make?}Đây là thứ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Well, uh...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:21.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Simple All-In-One Shampoo, I guess?}Dầu gội đa năng...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.88,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{When Mom steps out for work,}Khi ba mẹ đi làm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.04,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Turi and I have to watch the house.}Turi và mình trông nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Hey, Dad forgot to take this!}A, ba quên thứ này rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Isn't that what he was rushing \NMom to make earlier?}Là mấy món ba nhắc mẹ chuẩn bị hồi sớm mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.95,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah. She'll get real mad if she finds out.}Ừm, mẹ biết được là bực lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,{And he'll need it, too.}Và ba cũng gặp rắc rối nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,{We should go deliver it to him.}Chúng ta phải đưa cho ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main, do you think you can walk to the gate?}Myne, em có thể đi ra đến cổng được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.44,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?}Em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.68,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{No wonder Mom insisted \Non the piggyback ride.}Thảo nào mẹ hay cõng mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.81,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Maybe we shouldn't do this.}Hay là quay lại thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.93,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You can't handle it yet.}Em vẫn chưa đủ sức đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll be fine...}Em ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{if we walk... nice and slowly...}nếu đi từ từ là ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.97,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Huh? Turi?}Turi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:17.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Ralph? Lutz and Fey, too.}Ralph? Lutz và Fey nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wow, check out this rainbow hair squad.}Ồ, tóc đủ màu luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Are you going to the forest?}Mấy cậu đi vào rừng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.06,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Yeah. What are you doing?}Ừm, còn cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:28.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,{We were thinking of heading to the gate \Nto deliver something Dad forgot to take.}Bọn tớ đến cổng đưa đồ cho ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Are they neighbors?}Hàng xóm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:35.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I knew it.}Chắc vậy rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.71,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Ralph, the redhead, is \Nthe same age as Turi.}Ralph, anh tóc đỏ, bằng tuổi Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.65,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{He's the third of four brothers.}Là anh thứ 3 trong 4 anh em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.45,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Fey's the same age, too. \NHe's Ralph's cousin.}Fey cũng bằng tuổi, là em họ Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.77,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Lutz, the blond, is Ralph's little brother.}Lutz, tóc vàng, em trai Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.97,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{He's five like I am now, huh?}Bằng tuổi mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.22,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main! Are you okay?}Myne! Em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:03.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I just got a little dizzy.}Chỉ hơi choáng váng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.03,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I can't even get up after a fall.}Mình thậm chí không dậy nổi sau khi té...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.93,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{This body really is frail.}Cơ thể này quá yếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.83,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Main, you okay?}Myne, cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.05,Default,L,0,0,0,,{You're going to the gate, right?\N I'll give you a ride.}Định đi ra cổng hả? Để tớ cõng cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.45,Default,R,0,0,0,,{You can't handle it yet.}Em vẫn chưa đủ sức đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.12,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I can, too.}Được mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.63,Default,R,0,0,0,,{I'll carry her.}Để anh làm cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.00,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Come on.}Nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thanks for offering, Lutz.}Cảm ơn nhé Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,{But Ralph's used to it, \Nso let him carry her.}Nhưng Ralph đã quen rồi nên để cậu ấy làm cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.78,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Lutz, it made me happy to see \Nyou were so worried about me.}Lutz, cảm ơn vì đã lo lắng cho tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.41,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You're so nice. Thank you.}Cậu tốt bụng thật đó, cảm ơn nha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Ralph, how are you holding up?}Ralph, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.42,Default,R,0,0,0,,{All good. Main's tiny and light.}Không sao, Myne nhỏ xíu và nhẹ hều.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.42,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thank you, really.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.36,Default,R,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.83,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Oh? Ralphy, my dear boy, dost thou \Nhave the hots for sister mine?}Ồ, ra là vậy. Tên Ralph này thích chị mình à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.32,Default,R,0,0,0,,Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.05,Default,R,0,0,0,,{You smell really nice.}Cậu thơm thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Do I?}Thế à...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.79,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Squee!}Gớm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Did you hear that, Mrs. Rubbernecker? \N"You smell really nice," he says!}"Cậu thơm thật đó?" Hắn nói thế đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What is he, the hero in a shoujo manga?!}Cứ như nhân vật chính trong shoujo manga ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.65,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Well, I did wash Turi's hair for her.}Turi xài dầu gội của mình mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.33,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{She looks prettier now, right?}Chị ấy dễ thương quá, phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.44,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Even my hair's all silky now!}Tóc chị cũng mượt hơn kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.88,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it smells great.}Ừm, thơm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.39,Flashback,M,0,0,0,,{Okay, time to dump this.}Rồi, đổ đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.21,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.14,Flashback,E,0,0,0,,{Hold it!}Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.90,Flashback,T,0,0,0,,{Mom?}Mẹ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.86,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I didn't expect Mom to be so conscious \Nof her appearance, though.}Không ngờ mẹ cũng thích chưng diện.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.52,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Your hair smells nice, too.}Tóc cậu cũng thơm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:17.15,Default,L,0,0,0,,{And you look prettier now that your hair's \Ntied up and doesn't cover your face.}Và khi buộc tóc gọn lại trông cậu dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What in the blue hell was that?!}Cái gì thế trời!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:31.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I've never had anyone do that to me in all \Nmy years, so I don't know how to respond!}Chưa có ai làm điều đó với mình nên biết phản ứng thế nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.34,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm a modest and shy wallflower!}Mình là một bông hoa nhút nhát!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This world is gonna give me a heart attack!}Thế giới này làm mình chết mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.32,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Main.}Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.97,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Look, we've made it to the south gate.}Chúng ta đến cổng Nam rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Dad.}Ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.11,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Turi? What's the matter?}Turi? Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You forgot this.}Ba quên cái này.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.53,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank you!}A, cảm ơn con!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.41,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Lutz and the others split off \Nand continued to the forest,}Lutz và mọi người tiếp tục đi vào rừng,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.52,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{while we went inside the gate.}còn bọn tôi thì vào trong cổng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.92,Default,G,0,0,0,,{They brought you something you forgot? \NYour daughters are very nice.}Mấy đứa mang đồ cho ba à? Ngoan thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.43,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Aren't they?}Còn gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.92,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{That's my daughters, the cutest \Nand smartest girls in the world!}Con gái tôi đấy, dễ thương và thông minh nhất thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.25,Default,G,0,0,0,,{There goes the captain, bragging \Nabout his girls again.}Đội trưởng lại bắt đầu màn khoe con gái rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.55,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{I love you two so much!}Dễ thương quá đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Stop that!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Dad, did something happen?}Ba, có chuyện gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.69,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{A VIP must've showed up.}À, có vẻ là một vị khách VIP.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Like who?}Là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:44.32,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Like a noble whose arrival we'd \Nhave to inform the lord about,}Ví dụ như một quý tộc nào đó đến và\N chúng ta phải thông báo cho lãnh chúa biết,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.27,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{or something like that.}hay đại loại vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.09,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Captain.}Đội trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.52,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.46,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Is that the salute here?}Kiểu chào ở thế giới này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.04,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Give me your report, Otto.}Báo cáo đi, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.65,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Count Lowenhardt asks that \Nthe gates be opened.}Bá tước Lowenhardt yêu cầu mở cổng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.08,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{His seal?}Con dấu đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.41,Default,O,0,0,0,,{It checked out.}Tôi đã xác nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.76,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{All right. Let him through.}Rồi, mở cổng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.41,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Dad's so cool when he's in work mode.}Ba lúc làm việc ngầu thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.24,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{That's paper!}Là giấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.66,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Actual writing!}Đang viết kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Main, don't get in the way of work.}Myne, đừng có cản trở.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad, what's this?}Ba, đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.29,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's parchment.}Là giấy da.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.79,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Paper made from goat and sheep skin.}Giấy làm từ da cừu hoặc dê.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Parchment...}Giấy da...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I beg you, Dad.}Ba, con muốn nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Please buy some for me.}Mua cho con đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.51,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I really need it!}Con thực sự cần nó mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:58.17,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{It's not something for kids to play with.}Nó không phải đồ chơi của con nít.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.91,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Besides, you don't know \Nhow to read or write.}Cơ mà con có biết đọc hay viết gì đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.57,Default,O,0,0,0,,{But, Captain, you aren't \Ngreat at writing yourself.}Nhưng anh cũng có giỏi việc viết lách đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What? You can't write?}Hả? Ba không viết được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.77,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{A soldier's job is to maintain \Nlaw and order in town!}C-Công việc của người lính là duy trì luật pháp và trật tự.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:21.96,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{As long as we know how to write \Npeople's names, that's enough.}Chỉ cần biết viết tên người là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.17,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll learn.}Con sẽ học viết chữ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Will you buy it for me then?}Rồi ba sẽ mua nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:30.38,Default,Tu,0,0,0,,{Each one costs a whole month's salary. \NI can't spend that much on a kid.}Một tờ giấy giá bằng cả tháng lương đó.\NBa không thể mua nổi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A whole month?!} Tháng lương?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:35.82,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Also, they don't sell paper \Nin shops commoners frequent.}Và họ cũng không bán giấy cho thường dân đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.86,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Down with poverty!}Mình ghét sự nghèo khó!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.68,Default,O,0,0,0,,{If you want to learn how to read \Nand write, why not use a slate?}Nếu muốn học viết, sao cháu không sử dụng bảng viết?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:51.32,Default,O,0,0,0,,{If you don't mind using my \Nold one, you can have it.}Nếu được thì chú sẽ cho cháu mấy món\N ngày xưa mình dùng để học.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.96,sign_Slate,Sign,0,0,0,,{Slate}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Are you sure?}Được ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.95,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I'll bring it with me sometime.}Ừm, lần sau chú sẽ mang cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Mister Otto!}Cảm ơn chú Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Please teach me how to read and write!}Hãy dạy cháu đọc viết nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.93,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Sure thing, Main.}Ừm, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm counting on you!}Nhờ cả vào chú!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.11,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You got it.}Cứ để chú lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I love you, Mister Otto!}Cháu yêu chú nhất Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.68,Default_Top,M,0,0,0,,{Hooray!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.66,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:20.02,Eyecatch_an4,Gu,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.99,Eyecatch_an6,Gu,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.93,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{As fall nears its end,}Mùa thu kết thúc,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.46,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{people here start preparing \Nfor the long winter ahead.}Mọi người bắt đầu chuẩn bị cho mùa đông lạnh lẽo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.76,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Inundated with winter prep work, I had\Nno time to spare for bookmaking.}Mình phải làm việc suốt để chuẩn bị cho\N mùa đông nên không có thời gian làm sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:41.56,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And today is "Dona, Dona"—}Và hôm nay "Dona, Dona--"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:44.81,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I mean, pork stocking day.}À không, là ngày mua thịt heo trữ đông.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.93,Default,T,0,0,0,,{It's like a festival. You'll have fun.}Cứ như lễ hội vậy, nó vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,{We all butcher pigs together,}Mọi người cùng nhau làm thịt heo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,{then brine and smoke the meat, \Nor make pot roast and sausages.}sau đó ngâm muối rồi xông khói hoặc nướng và làm xúc xích.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,{We won't last the winter otherwise.}Nếu không sẽ không qua được mùa đông đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Butchering pigs...}Mổ thịt heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:03.44,Default,E,0,0,0,,{I hope Main doesn't develop a \Nfever midway like last year.}Hi vọng Myne không sốt giữa đường như năm ngoái.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.44,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I wish I had developed a fever again.}Mình thì đang mong bị sốt lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's so different than being in town!}Khác hẳn so với trong thị trấn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{And the air is so fresh! I feel alive again!}Không khí thật trong thành! Mình cảm thấy thật sảng khoái!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.71,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Main, keep your mouth shut, \Nor you'll bite your tongue.}Myne, đang đi đừng nói, cắn vào lưỡi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You need asphalt roads!}Sao không có đường nhựa hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.29,Default,W,0,0,0,,{We've only got sons, so...}Bọn tôi chỉ toàn con trai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:21.50,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I was told to watch from afar since \Nthey didn't want me bothering them.}Mình chỉ ngồi xem ở phía xa để không cản trở mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:27.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Not that I mind. This gives \Nme time to brainstorm.}Mà kệ đi. Ngồi đây yên tĩnh dễ suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Both books and paper are \Ntoo expensive to buy.}Cả sách và giấy đều quá mắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Then I'll have to start \Nby making my own paper!}Vậy thì mình tự làm giấy luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:40.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But how am I supposed to?}Nhưng mà... làm sao giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{There's no way I can chop down \Ntrees with my own hands.}Đôi tay này thì sao chặt cây được chứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.01,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Hold it!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ugh, how primitive.}Thật lạc hậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:54.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. What did they do before \Nall the machinery was invented?}A, họ đã làm gì trước khi máy móc được phát minh ra nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:58.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ancient civilizations... Ancient Egypt...}Nền văn minh cổ đại... Ai Cập cổ đại...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,Giấy cói!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:05.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Even if I can't make papyrus, I should be \Nable to weave something out of grass fiber!}Dù mình không thể làm giấy cói nhưng\N vẫn có thể dệt thứ gì đó từ cỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:09.94,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I'll make pseudo-papyrus \Nand make a book out of that!}Mình sẽ làm giấy giả cói và viết sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.15,Default,Gu,0,0,0,,{Here I go.}Lên đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Where am I?}Đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.20,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad you came to.}May quá, cháu tỉnh rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.91,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto?}Chú Otto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.94,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You remember me?}Còn nhớ chú à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How could I forget?}Sao quên được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.10,Default,O,0,0,0,,{How do you feel? Better now?}Cháu thấy khỏe hơn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.97,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Uh...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.71,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Why am I here?}Tại sao cháu ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.97,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You fainted during pork stocking.}Tự nhiên cháu ngất ra khi đang mổ heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.03,Default,O,0,0,0,,{The captain brought you here in a panic.}Đội trưởng đã mang cháu đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.76,Default,O,0,0,0,,{He said they'll pick you \Nup once they're done.}Anh ấy sẽ đến đón khi nào xong việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.66,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Are you lonely?}Cháu buồn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:37.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,{No. I was just wondering \Nhow I should kill time.}Không, cháu đang tìm trò giết thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:43.16,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Right, he did say you were \Nolder than you looked.}Phải rồi, đội trưởng bảo cháu già hơn so với tuổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.90,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Give me a minute.}Chờ chú nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.64,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Will this help you pass the time?}Cái này giết thời gian được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:54.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A slate!}Bảng viết!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.25,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I said I'd give you mine, didn't I?}Chú hứa cho cháu rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:03.73,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.24,Default,O,0,0,0,,{That's your name.}Tên cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:12.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{So this is how my name's written.}Vậy đây là tên cháu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.27,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I'll have to get back to work, so \Nwhy don't you practice with that?}Chú phải quay lại làm việc nên là luyện tập đi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:25.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{M... a... i... n...}M...y...n...e
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm so excited!}Phấn khích quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Actual letters!}Là chữ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Fun!}Vui quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.70,sign_slate2_dog,Sign,0,0,0,,{The quick brown fox jumps\Nover the lazy dog}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This is so much fun!}Vui quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.21,sign_slate3_name,Sign,0,0,0,,Motosu Urano
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Motosu Urano, huh?}Motosu Urano à...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:18.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But that's not my name anymore.}Không còn là của mình nữa nhỉ...
