Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.64,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Main, the captain's back for you.}Myne, đội trưởng quay lại rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:17.40,sign_slate5_hot,Sign,0,0,0,,{So hot}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:17.39,Default_Top,O,0,0,0,,{B-Big trouble, Captain! It's Main!}Đ-Đội trưởng, Myne--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,{You have a fever again, huh?}Em lại sốt nữa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:26.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I know we haven't finished\Npreparing for winter yet.}Xin lỗi... Chúng ta vẫn chưa chuẩn bị xong cho mùa đông...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,{That's some of the sausage\Nwe all made together.}Đó là súp xúc xích mọi người cùng nhau làm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This is good.}Ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:46.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Turi, this sausage is really delicious!}Turi, món này ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:50.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yeah? Well, you better sleep \Nonce you're done eating.}Thế hả? Ăn xong thì ngủ ngoan nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.54,Default,M,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The soup does need improvement, though.}Món súp này có lẽ cần cải thiện hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That was great.}Cảm ơn vì món ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Look at how happy I'm feeling \Njust by being able to write.}Vui vì đã viết chữ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:22.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'd probably be on cloud nine \Nif I could read an actual book.}Nếu được đọc sách chắc mình vui chết mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:34.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh? Wait, didn't I hit upon a \Ngreat idea before I fainted?}Ủa? Cơ mà trước khi ngất thì mình nghĩ\N ra ý tưởng gì hay lắm thì phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.93,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What was it?}Là gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.45,Next_Chapter,,0,0,0,,{Next Chapter\N}{\fs24}{The Events of Winter}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:17.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Papyrus, damn it! Papyrus!}Giấy cói! Là giấy cói!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.31,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm such a klutz!}Mình đúng là ngốc mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.58,Default,F,0,0,0,,{That's nothing new.}Giờ mới biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:25.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,{That aside, I didn't expect the AIO Shampoo \Nto make an appearance this early.}Cơ mà cha không ngờ dầu gội lại xuất hiện sớm như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:26.75,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:29.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But that's what leads to \Nmeeting the mercha—}Nhưng đó là những gì sẽ dẫn chúng ta đến--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.32,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Spoilers again?}Cấm spoiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.46,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Will you ever learn?}Vẫn chưa trưởng thành rồi.
